PRINCESS CATHERINE STYLISH IN £6 ZARA SKIRT IN WALES
Princess Kate and Prince William are in south Wales for three events, beginning with a visit to the Brynawel Rehabilitation Centre near Pontyclun. The Princess wore a mid-length black and white houndstooth print skirt, similar to what Welsh women traditionally wear.

CROWN PRINCESS MARY SPORTS IN PAISLEY COAT AS VISIT MEDICAL INDIA INSTITUTE
Crown Princess Mary of Denmark attended the opening session of India-Denmark Partners for Green and Sustainable Progress today. Princess Mary wore her Etro reversible patterned coat, which costs a whopping £1,669.

QUEEN LETIZIA CHIC IN £158 OMBRÉ SKIRT IN MADRID
This morning, February 28, Queen Letizia and King Felipe were seen arriving at the Royal Academy of History in Madrid.  Queen Letizia looked stunning in a pink and black ensemble. The Spanish royal was dressed in a light pink turtleneck sweater with long sleeves and a close fit. She wore it with a mid-length pleated skirt that she accessorized with a thick black belt.
